## الإطار المفاهيمي — Unified BOM / Conceptual Framework

كل وكيل AIX هو نقطة مركزية في graph من أربع طبقات:
Every AIX agent is the central node in a 4-layer graph:

```
Agent (AIX manifest)
      │
      ├─── SaaS Layer        → saas_refs[]
      │    ├── CRM, Ticketing, Logging
      │    ├── LLM APIs, Vector DBs
      │    ├── OAuth apps, Webhooks
      │    └── PII / Health / Finance data exposure
      │
      ├─── AI / Model Layer  → ai_refs[]
      │    ├── model provider (OpenAI, Anthropic, HF, internal)
      │    ├── model type (LLM, Embedding, Vision, Reranker)
      │    ├── training / fine-tune / RAG datasets
      │    └── risk flags (poisoning, unknown provenance)
      │
      ├─── ABOM Layer        → abom.constituents[]
      │    ├── tools, libraries, frameworks
      │    ├── dependencies with licenses
      │    └── SBOM-compatible entries
      │
      └─── Infra Layer       → infra_refs[]
           ├── Cloud functions / containers
           ├── Databases, queues, storage
           └── deployment bindings
```

هذا الربط يجعل AIX قادرًا على الإجابة على:
This binding enables AIX to answer:
> **AR**: "ما هو كل شيء يعتمد عليه هذا الوكيل؟ وما مستوى مخاطره؟ وهل هو جاهز للامتثال؟"
> **EN**: "What does this agent depend on? What is its risk level? Is it compliance-ready?"

