## حقول Schema المقترحة / Proposed Schema Extension

أضف هذا القسم إلى أي AIX manifest:
Add this section to any AIX manifest:

```json
{
  "unified_bom": {
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "generated_at": "<ISO-8601 timestamp>",
    "saas_refs": [
      {
        "id": "saas:salesforce-crm",
        "name": "Salesforce CRM",
        "category": "CRM",
        "integration": "REST API",
        "data_sensitivity": ["PII", "Business"],
        "dpa_documented": true
      }
    ],
    "ai_refs": [
      {
        "id": "model:openai-gpt4o",
        "provider": "OpenAI",
        "model_type": "LLM",
        "endpoint": "https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions",
        "dataset_provenance": "unknown",
        "risk_flags": ["external_provider", "no_audit_log"]
      }
    ],
    "infra_refs": [
      {
        "id": "infra:vercel-fn-contract-review",
        "type": "serverless_function",
        "platform": "Vercel",
        "region": "iad1",
        "bound_agent": "<aix_agent_id>"
      }
    ],
    "compliance_profiles": ["EU_AI_ACT", "CISA_SBOM"],
    "risk_summary": {
      "overall": "HIGH",
      "use_case_classification": "high_risk",
      "open_gaps": ["missing_dpa", "incomplete_ai_sbom"]
    },
    "export_artifacts": [
      "sbom.cdx.json",
      "ai-sbom.json",
      "saas-bom.json",
      "compliance-bundle-eu-ai-act.zip"
    ]
  }
}
```

**AR — Tradeoff**: يمكن دمج هذه البيانات داخل `abom.constituents` لتقليل التكرار، لكن قسم `unified_bom` المستقل أوضح للتقارير متعددة الطبقات.
**EN — Tradeoff**: Merging into `abom.constituents` reduces duplication, but a standalone `unified_bom` section is clearer for multi-layer compliance reports and auditors.

