## مكوّنات التنفيذ / Implementation Components

### 1. Schema → `schemas/`
```
schemas/unified-bom.schema.json   # JSON Schema for unified_bom extension
schemas/saas-ref.schema.json      # SaaS reference object definition
schemas/ai-ref.schema.json        # AI/model reference object definition
```

### 2. Core → `core/`
```
core/unified-bom/collector.ts     # Reads AIX manifests → builds BOM graph
core/unified-bom/correlator.ts    # Links SaaS + AI + Infra refs
core/unified-bom/risk-engine.ts   # Calculates risk score → generates findings
core/unified-bom/exporter.ts      # Outputs compliance bundles
```

### 3. CI → `.github/workflows/`
```yaml
- name: Generate Unified BOM
  run: node scripts/generate-unified-bom.mjs

- name: Sign BOM (SLSA provenance)
  uses: sigstore/cosign-action@v3
  with:
    args: sign-blob ./dist/unified-bom.json

- name: Upload BOM artifact
  uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
  with:
    name: unified-bom
    path: ./dist/unified-bom.json
```

### 4. MCP Server → `packages/mcp-server`
```typescript
tools: [
  {
    name: "list_unified_bom",
    description: "Returns the full Unified BOM for a given AIX agent ID",
    // AR: يعيد الـ BOM الكامل لوكيل AIX محدد
    inputSchema: { agent_id: "string" }
  },
  {
    name: "export_compliance_bundle",
    description: "Exports a compliance-ready artifact bundle",
    // AR: يصدّر حزمة امتثال جاهزة للمراجعة
    inputSchema: { agent_id: "string", framework: "EU_AI_ACT | CISA | NIST" }
  },
  {
    name: "trace_data_lineage",
    description: "Traces all datasets linked to an agent and their provenance",
    // AR: يتتبع كل البيانات المرتبطة بالوكيل ومصادرها
    inputSchema: { agent_id: "string" }
  },
  {
    name: "explain_risk_posture",
    description: "Returns risk summary and open gaps for a given agent",
    // AR: يعيد ملخص المخاطر والفجوات المفتوحة
    inputSchema: { agent_id: "string" }
  }
]
```

