## قواعد الأمن / Security Rules

| Risk Point | AIX Source | AR | EN Remediation |
|---|---|---|---|
| Unknown SaaS deps | `saas_refs` incomplete | اكتشاف تلقائي | Auto-discovery via SSPM |
| Hidden model providers | `ai_refs` missing | إلزام `ai_refs` في validation | Require `ai_refs` in CI gate |
| Untracked datasets | `abom.constituents` | أضف dataset entries | Add dataset entries to ABOM |
| PII exposure | `saas_refs[].data_sensitivity` | تحقق من DPA | Verify DPA for each PII SaaS |
| Unsigned artifacts | `export_artifacts` | توقيع Sigstore / SLSA | Sigstore / SLSA provenance |
| Policy drift | `security` vs runtime | CI security gate | CI security gate diff check |

